2 Days Ago Meanwhile, Governor Nasir El-Rufai has sent his condolences to the families of the deceased students. He condemned the killing of the three students, describing it as wickedness, inhumanity and an outright desecration of human lives by vile entities. He also described the armed bandits as the worst of humankind who must be hunted down for their atrocities.